PrecisAppointment of two TEMPORARY ADMINISTRATORS who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of NEWFOUNDLAND during his absence, illness or other inability, the first being the Hon. T. ALEXANDER HICKMAN, who will act for a twelve-day period (Feb. 28 - March 10, 1992), and the other being the Hon. JAMES R. GUSHUE, who will act for a five-day period (March 16 - 20, 1992).
